{"id":235,"ayahs":[{"number":118,"arabic":"وَلَوْ شَآءَ رَبُّكَ لَجَعَلَ ٱلنَّاسَ أُمَّةًۭ وَٰحِدَةًۭ ۖ وَلَا يَزَالُونَ مُخْتَلِفِينَ","translation":"And had thy Sustainer so willed, He could surely have made all mankind one single community: but [He willed it otherwise, and so] they continue to hold divergent views'","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1591.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":76070,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَوْ","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76071,"position":2,"arabic":"شَآءَ","translation":"ইচ্ছে করতেন","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76072,"position":3,"arabic":"رَبُّكَ","translation":"তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76073,"position":4,"arabic":"لَجَعَلَ","translation":"অবশ্যই বানাতে পারতেন","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76074,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسَ","translation":"সব মানুষকে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76075,"position":6,"arabic":"أُمَّةًۭ","translation":"জাতি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76076,"position":7,"arabic":"وَٰحِدَةًۭ ۖ","translation":"একই","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76078,"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"কিন্তু (তবুও) না","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76079,"position":9,"arabic":"يَزَالُونَ","translation":"তারা সর্বদা হতো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76080,"position":10,"arabic":"مُخْتَلِفِينَ","translation":"মতবিরোধকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/011_118_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76081,"position":11,"arabic":"١١٨","translation":"(১১৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":119,"arabic":"إِلَّا مَن رَّحِمَ رَبُّكَ ۚ وَلِذَٰلِكَ خَلَقَهُمْ ۗ وَتَمَّتْ كَلِمَةُ رَبِّكَ لَأَمْلَأَنَّ جَهَنَّمَ مِنَ ٱلْجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ أَجْمَعِينَ","translation":"[all of them,] save those upon whom thy Sustainer has bestowed His grace. And to this end has He created them [all. But [as for those who refuse to avail themselves of divine guidance,] that word of thy Sustainer shall be fulfilled: \"Most certainly will I fill hell with invisible beings as well as with humans, all together!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1592.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":76286,"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"তবে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76287,"position":2,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76288,"position":3,"arabic":"رَّحِمَ","translation":"অনুগ্রহ করতেন","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76289,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبُّكَ ۚ","translation":"তোমার রব (সেটা ভিন্ন কথা)","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76291,"position":5,"arabic":"وَلِذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এবং এ কারণে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76292,"position":6,"arabic":"خَلَقَهُمْ ۗ","translation":"তাদের সৃষ্টি করেছেন (স্বাধীনতা দিয়ে)","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76294,"position":7,"arabic":"وَتَمَّتْ","translation":"এবং (এভাবে) সম্পূর্ণ হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76295,"position":8,"arabic":"كَلِمَةُ","translation":"একটি বাণী","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76296,"position":9,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","translation":"তোমার রবের (যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76297,"position":10,"arabic":"لَأَمْلَأَنَّ","translation":"\"অবশ্যই ভরে দিবো আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76298,"position":11,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ","translation":"জাহান্নামকে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76299,"position":12,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76300,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلْجِنَّةِ","translation":"জিন","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76301,"position":14,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّاسِ","translation":"এবং মানুষ","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76302,"position":15,"arabic":"أَجْمَعِينَ","translation":"একত্রেই\"","audioUrl":"wbw/011_119_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76303,"position":16,"arabic":"١١٩","translation":"(১১৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":120,"arabic":"وَكُلًّۭا نَّقُصُّ عَلَيْكَ مِنْ أَنۢبَآءِ ٱلرُّسُلِ مَا نُثَبِّتُ بِهِۦ فُؤَادَكَ ۚ وَجَآءَكَ فِى هَٰذِهِ ٱلْحَقُّ وَمَوْعِظَةٌۭ وَذِكْرَىٰ لِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"AND [remember:] out of all the accounts relating to the [earlier] apostles We convey unto thee [only] that wherewith We [aim to] make firm thy heart: for through these [accounts] comes the truth unto thee, as well as an admonition and a reminder unto all believers.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1593.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":76356,"position":1,"arabic":"وَكُلًّۭا","translation":"এবং সব (কিছুই)","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76357,"position":2,"arabic":"نَّقُصُّ","translation":"আমরা বর্ণনা করছি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76358,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْكَ","translation":"তোমার কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76359,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76360,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنۢبَآءِ","translation":"সংবাদ","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76361,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلرُّسُلِ","translation":"রাসূলদের","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76362,"position":7,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76363,"position":8,"arabic":"نُثَبِّتُ","translation":"আমরা সুদৃঢ় করছি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76364,"position":9,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"তা দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76365,"position":10,"arabic":"فُؤَادَكَ ۚ","translation":"তোমার হৃদয়কে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76367,"position":11,"arabic":"وَجَآءَكَ","translation":"এবং তোমার কাছে এসেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76368,"position":12,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76369,"position":13,"arabic":"هَـٰذِهِ","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76370,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلْحَقُّ","translation":"প্রকৃত সত্য","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76371,"position":15,"arabic":"وَمَوْعِظَةٌۭ","translation":"এবং উপদেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76372,"position":16,"arabic":"وَذِكْرَىٰ","translation":"ও সাবধান বাণী","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76373,"position":17,"arabic":"لِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"মু'মিনদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_120_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76374,"position":18,"arabic":"١٢٠","translation":"(১২০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":121,"arabic":"وَقُل لِّلَّذِينَ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ ٱعْمَلُوا۟ عَلَىٰ مَكَانَتِكُمْ إِنَّا عَٰمِلُونَ","translation":"And say unto those who will not believe: \"Do anything that may be within your power, [while] we, behold, shall labour [in God's way];","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1594.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":76610,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقُل","translation":"এবং বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76611,"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের জন্যে) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76612,"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76613,"position":4,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"ঈমান আনে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76614,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱعْمَلُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা কাজ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76615,"position":6,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76616,"position":7,"arabic":"مَكَانَتِكُمْ","translation":"তোমদের জায়গার","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76617,"position":8,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরাও","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76618,"position":9,"arabic":"عَـٰمِلُونَ","translation":"কাজ করে যাচ্ছি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_121_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76619,"position":10,"arabic":"١٢١","translation":"(১২১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":122,"arabic":"وَٱنتَظِرُوٓا۟ إِنَّا مُنتَظِرُونَ","translation":"and wait [for what is coming]: behold, we too are waiting!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1595.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":76728,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱنتَظِرُوٓا۟","translation":"এবং তোমরা অপেক্ষা করো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_122_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76729,"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরাও","audioUrl":"wbw/011_122_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76730,"position":3,"arabic":"مُنتَظِرُونَ","translation":"প্রতীক্ষাকারী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/011_122_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76731,"position":4,"arabic":"١٢٢","translation":"(১২২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":123,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ غَيْبُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ وَإِلَيْهِ يُرْجَعُ ٱلْأَمْرُ كُلُّهُۥ فَٱعْبُدْهُ وَتَوَكَّلْ عَلَيْهِ ۚ وَمَا رَبُّكَ بِغَٰفِلٍ عَمَّا تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"And God alone comprehends the hidden reality of the heavens and the earth: for, all that exists goes back to Him [as its source]. Worship Him, then, and place thy trust in Him alone: for thy Sustainer is not unaware of what you do.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1596.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":76919,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহর (আছে জ্ঞান)","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76920,"position":2,"arabic":"غَيْبُ","translation":"অদৃশ্যের","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76921,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76922,"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76923,"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِلَيْهِ","translation":"এবং তাঁরই দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76924,"position":6,"arabic":"يُرْجَعُ","translation":"ফিরিয়ে আনা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76925,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَمْرُ","translation":"ব্যাপার","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76926,"position":8,"arabic":"كُلُّهُۥ","translation":"সবই","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76927,"position":9,"arabic":"فَٱعْبُدْهُ","translation":"অতএব তাঁরই ইবাদত করো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76928,"position":10,"arabic":"وَتَوَكَّلْ","translation":"ভরসা করো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76929,"position":11,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ ۚ","translation":"তাঁরই উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76931,"position":12,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং নন","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76932,"position":13,"arabic":"رَبُّكَ","translation":"তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/011_123_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76933,"position":14,"arabic":"بِغَـٰفِلٍ","transl